Class AuthenticateActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jonathancarlton.authenticateapp.AuthenticateActivity

  • public class AuthenticateActivity
extends java.lang.Object

    Authenticate Activity

    The activity in which the user is greeted with the button to authenticate themselves - if successful they are able to do a range of things (constructs that aren't built into this program) i.e. access a room.
